==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''slander'''
# a [[false]] or [[malicious]] [[statement]], especially one which is [[injurious]] to a person's [[reputation]]
# a false spoken statement about someone which damages their [[reputation]], or the making of such a [[statement]]

